{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_therex_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_therex_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"炙热冲击！","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在一次外勤任务中，Thermal-EX的表现超越了博士的预期。机器人的行为不再符合计算结果，这或许不是一个巧合。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_therex_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["工程干员","可露希尔","医药公司代表","Thermal-EX","干员直尺","斑点","守林人","黑帮A","黑帮B","梅尔"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"个人剧情 Thermal-EX","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Text","text":"2:30 P. M. 天气/晴","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"罗德岛本舰 总工程师办公室","id":9},{"type":"Dialog","id":10},{"type":"Character","id":11},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_motorroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":13},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_088","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"老大，这是这个月船上各区的线路安全报告。","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"dialog","id":17},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"嗯，嗯......没什么问题。","id":20,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"嗯？这里有一点小波动。","id":21,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"——凌晨两点到早上六点，每一天晚上都有相似的异常？这个区域是宿舍区吧？","id":22,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"2","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"是宿舍区。这么一说，我也想起来了，开始那几天，那附近还有人报告过停电。","id":24,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"我们过去一看，线路都是好的，只是单位时间输出功率超阈值了。","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":26},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"啊嚏——呃，说起来，办公室是不是有点冷？","id":28,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"2","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"是有一点。","id":30,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"应该说这段时间一直都有点冷......室内温度是不是该再调高点？","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"忍忍吧，节能比较重要！","id":33,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"说正经的，这些异常，看来应该又是哪个小坏蛋偷偷使用违规电器吧。","id":34,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"对了老大，那几次我去检查，在走廊附近看到了Thermal-EX。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咦？难道不是违规电器，是电器违规？","id":38,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"工程干员","text":"要我去把Thermal-EX叫来吗？","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_088"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"先看看他在哪里。干员日志......找到啦。","id":42,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":43},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"啊，Thermal-EX现在正在叙拉古出外勤？同行人里面有——博士？！","id":45,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"呃，这倒是，没想到......","id":46,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"唔......","id":48,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_088","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"算啦，就算有问题，也肯定是小问题，应该还好吧？博士在的话，就算出问题也能搞定的啦。","id":50,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"等他们回来，再去找凯尔希问问情况好了。","id":51,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":52},{"type":"Character","id":53},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_offce","screenadapt":"coverall","id":55},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"Text","text":"叙拉古拉克玛蒂瓦 罗德岛办事处","id":57},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"合同条款没什么问题了，麻烦您千里迢迢跑这一趟。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"这次有机会见到罗德岛的博士，真是意外的荣幸。也请您回去之后，向阿米娅女士转达我们的谢意。","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"64","text":"这都是应该的。"},{"id":"64","text":"偶尔出来溜达下挺好。"}],"values":[],"id":63},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"接下来，只需要您将药物配方和样品交给我——","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"67","text":"Thermal-EX。"}],"values":[],"id":66},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":67,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":69},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"嗷嗷！终于轮到我闪亮登场了吗？","id":71,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"说、说话了？！我还以为这只是个长得有些吓人的机器......","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"诞生于雷神工业最新技术，经天才的可露希尔和伟大的梅尔携手改造，我是这个时代最完美的机——器——人！","id":76,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"这位先生，您的惊讶我非常理解。","id":77,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"顺便提一句，我能做到的事超乎你的想象，请您注视着我炙热的身体，不要眨眼，我将会为您表演光与热的魔术——","id":78,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"80","text":"咳咳，Thermal-EX。"}],"values":[],"id":79},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":80},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"博士，您又在呼唤我吗？我知道您需要我，只要您一声令下，我什么都能为您做到。","id":82,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"84","text":"我正要说。"},{"id":"84","text":"......"},{"id":"84","text":"我想让你继续保持沉默。"}],"values":[],"id":83},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":84},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"了解了！Thermal-EX，即刻切断控制链接——","id":86,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":87},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"等下等下，也不用直接关机吧！！","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"咳咳。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"博士，这十张便携式源石软盘已经准备好了。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"这些就是本次交易的药物配方吗？","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"95","text":"稍等。"}],"values":[],"id":94},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":95},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"唔噢，唔唔唔噢！","id":97,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"99","text":"等Thermal-EX完成数据传输，这些资料就能交给你，代表先生。"}],"values":[],"id":98},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":99,"end":105},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"真是奇妙的机器......呃，机器人！罗德岛果然不同凡响，不仅仅在医药领域，连工程技术也如此杰出。","id":101,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"谢谢！您的眼光同样不同凡响！这热烈的夸奖让我更有动力了！","id":103,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"呵......呵呵......","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_028","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"108","text":"传输进度，百分之五十。"}],"values":[],"id":107},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":108},{"type":"Character","name":"char_284_spot_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"终于快要解脱了吗？我居然有一点点怀念A6那几个家伙了。","id":111,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"至少他们还会正常说话，不至于像这几位临时队友，不是惜字如金，就是聒噪个不停。","id":112,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"......","id":114,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"斑点先生，您昨天还靠在我身上烘干了被雨打湿的毛发，哪怕只有短短十分钟，与您拉近的距离依然让我燥热了起来！","id":116,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"咳咳。","id":118,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"120","text":"传输进度，百分之七十五。"}],"values":[],"id":119},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":120,"end":132},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"呼，这次合作真是超乎我想象的顺利——","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_158_milu","focus":"2","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"别说话。","id":124,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_158_milu","focus":"1","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"医药公司代表","text":"啊？","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_028"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_028","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"啧，这位朋友，你真是拥有一张十分幸运的嘴。","id":128,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"0.6","id":129},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"趴下！","id":132,"figure":"char_158_milu","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":133},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":134},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":136},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":138},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$chasing_intro","key":"$chasing_loop","volume":"0.4","id":139,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":140},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"什、什么？沿街那面的墙被炸开了？","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"啊，这熟悉的热量冲击！不过与我的能量相比，还是不值一提。","id":144,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"博士，有我挡在您面前，您应该没事吧？","id":145,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"147","text":"我没事。"},{"id":"147","text":"作为掩体，你矮了点。"}],"values":[],"id":146},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":147},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"看这源石炸弹的规模，是当地帮派干的。","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"这挺奇怪的，我们在这里活动这么久了，除了偶尔摩擦，基本相安无事。毕竟我们也会为他们提供一些药品。","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"嗷我知道了！他们一定是看上了我——毕竟哪里还有我这样完美华丽、热量满满的机器人呢？","id":152,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"有我在的话，他们根本就不需要这些粗糙的爆破物品了！","id":153,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_284_spot_1","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"......有时候我真怀疑他是月见夜的亲兄弟。","id":155,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"他有可能是对的。","id":157,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"哦？","id":159,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"有组织有计划的袭击，一定有明确的目标，并且在准确的时机。","id":161,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"163","text":"Thermal-EX携带的配方。"}],"values":[],"id":162},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":163},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"看来是交易信息泄露。","id":165,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":166},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"守林人小姐扫视着我们每一个人的眼神......有些可怕。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"打我朋友主意的人都不可原谅。","id":170,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"喂，说到配方，这个什么代表，他好像晕过去了。","id":172,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"也太弱了吧。站得离墙那么远，只是被吓到了而已。","id":173,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"都做好准备。有敌人靠近。五个。","id":175,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"177","text":"Thermal-EX——"}],"values":[],"id":176},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":177},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"好的博士，全部交给我吧！我的热情正在酝酿！","id":179,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"181","text":"——注意时机。"}],"values":[],"id":180},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":181,"end":183},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"来了。","id":183,"figure":"char_158_milu","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":184},{"type":"character","id":185},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":186},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"噢噢噢全力冲击！","id":188,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":189},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":191},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":192},{"type":"Dialog","id":193},{"type":"Character","id":194},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":195},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_offce","screenadapt":"coverall","id":196},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"全倒了。","id":200,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"还真是有效率......","id":202,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":203},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"呃......呃......炙热......炙......热......","id":205,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"......然而是个一波流。","id":207,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"Thermal-EX他还好吧？我有些听不懂他在说什么。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":210},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"炙......热......","id":212,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"214","text":"这是短时间内输出能量强度过高引起的其余功能模块暂时失灵。"},{"id":"214","text":"过几分钟就好，不必惊慌。"}],"values":[],"id":213},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":214},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"外面还有敌人。这一批人更多。","id":216,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"多也没事吧？我们难道干不倒？","id":218,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"我一个人就可以。","id":220,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","name2":"char_284_spot_1","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"......你看，甚至用不上复数词。","id":222,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"各位，后面还有一条路可以出去......毕竟这办事处之前也是安全屋。","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"226","text":"斑点，你和直尺带代表先生从安全通道撤退。"}],"values":[],"id":225},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":226},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":227},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"热......","id":229,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"博士，你们呢？Thermal-EX看起来没法正常工作。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"233","text":"我们留在这里。"}],"values":[],"id":232},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":233},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"干员直尺","text":"会不会有危险？","id":235,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_284_spot_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斑点","text":"走了走了，你听到命令了。","id":237,"figure":"char_284_spot_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"239","text":"守林人，隐蔽自己，注意指令。"}],"values":[],"id":238},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":239,"end":241},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"......好。","id":241,"figure":"char_158_milu","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":242},{"type":"character","id":243},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":244},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":245},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_031","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":249},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"咳，咳咳，这里面也太热了。爆破组那帮蠢货，又使劲过头了吧？","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"不许动——咦，就一个人？你一个，打趴下了五个？","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"255","text":"他们自己绊倒了。"},{"id":"255","text":"......"},{"id":"255","text":"对，都是我打趴下的。"}],"values":[],"id":254},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"你，你，还有你，你们仨给我看住这个人！","id":256,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"其他人去搜下屋子。记住，我们要找的应该是几张软盘。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_031","name2":"avg_npc_031","focus":"2","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮B","text":"报告！这里发现还有一个出口！","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"261","text":"要找配方的话，已经被那位代表先生带走了。"}],"values":[],"id":260},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":261},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_031","name2":"avg_npc_031","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"*叙拉古粗口*什么？！被他带走了？","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_031","name2":"avg_npc_031","focus":"2","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮B","text":"呃，这和说好的不一样啊......要不要去追？","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_031","name2":"avg_npc_031","focus":"1","id":267},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.4","text":"","id":268},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"追？追你个头啊！我们要的是在这些人手上的配方！已经拿到的话......算了算了！","id":270,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"这一趟总得拿点什么回去。配方没了，找找药什么的。都动作快点！","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":272},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"炙......热......","id":274,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"avg_npc_031","focus":"2","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"咦，这是什么玩意儿？那一闪一闪的，是源石制品吗？","id":276,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"278","text":"是万能药品制造机。"}],"values":[],"id":277},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":278},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_031","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"啊？我从来没听说过这种东西。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"282","text":"你们过来，我演示给你们看。"}],"values":[],"id":281},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"看你赤手空拳又文文弱弱，应该也耍不出什么花招。","id":283,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑帮A","text":"......倒让我看看这到底是个什么东西。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_031"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"287","text":"只需要一个指——"}],"values":[],"id":286},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":287},{"type":"Character","name":"char_158_milu","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"守林人","text":"（瞄准）","id":289,"figure":"char_158_milu"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":290},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"炙热！！！","id":292,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":293},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_explo_n","id":294},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":300},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":301},{"type":"Dialog","id":302},{"type":"Character","id":303},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_room_2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":305},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":306},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":307,"musicid":2},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":309},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"哇，博士，那些故事都是真的吗？","id":311,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"你在叙拉古一拳打趴五个黑帮分子，又一句话震趴下另外十个，并且拿那些人作为谈判筹码，给我们谈了个超级优惠大订单？","id":312,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"314","text":"打人的事都是Thermal-EX干的。"},{"id":"314","text":"......"},{"id":"314","text":"那家公司给我们设套，最后自作自受而已。"}],"values":[],"id":313},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":314},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"你也不用谦虚啦，守林人他们在跟凯尔希汇报的时候，我都听到了哦。","id":316,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"——在交易完成之前，与当地黑帮里应外合，从你们手中抢走配方和样品，就可以不花一分钱拿到东西。","id":317,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"同时在日后和罗德岛的交易中占据有利位置。","id":318,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这就是他们的如意算盘吧？","id":320,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"322","text":"所以他们需要挑交易完成前的时间点下手。"},{"id":"322","text":"所以那个医药公司的人才会适时晕倒。"},{"id":"322","text":"所以他们并不想追那些“已经”落到自己人手里的软盘。"}],"values":[],"id":321},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":322},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"不愧是你呀，博士，任务过程刺激得跟某些电视剧似的。真该和凯尔希说说，让你多出点外勤。","id":324,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","id":325},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"不过，整个事件里，的确有一件事很奇怪吧？","id":326,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"报告里写的，“博士精准地计算到了Thermal-EX恢复功能的时间，在最好的时机指挥Thermal-EX发起第二轮热力法术冲击”——","id":327,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"可是按照我的计算，那个时间点，应该还没有到Thermal-EX完全恢复的时间才对。","id":328,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"博士你本来，是想让其他干员来实施攻击的对不对？","id":330,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"332","text":"没错。"}],"values":[],"id":331},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":332},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"334","text":"这就是我来这里的原因。"}],"values":[],"id":333},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":334},{"type":"Dialog","id":335},{"type":"Character","id":336},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":337},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":338},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"0.6","id":340},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":341},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"晚上好，最天才的可露希尔小姐和最最闪亮的博士！","id":344,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":345},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"......为什么我只有一个最啊？！","id":347,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"伟大的梅尔小姐正在帮我检查身体，现在有了你们的加入，我感到自己更热了！","id":349,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"嗨，博士，你想再让我说一遍我们俩是如何在危急关头，通过完美的配合，打退那些试图染指我的叙拉古暴徒的故事吗？","id":350,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......停，Thermal-EX。这故事我听了好几遍了，虽说我这几天都几乎没出过工作室的门。","id":352,"figure":"char_242_mayer"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer","focus":"1","id":353},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"帅气的传言可不是门禁可以挡得住的啊，就跟帅气的我一样。","id":354,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#2","id":355},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波。","id":356,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":357},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"别、别咬我，我这次是和博士一起敲门进来的啊啊啊！！！","id":359,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"——打开Thermal-EX的能源模块面板。","id":361,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"早说不是冲我来的......","id":363,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#3","id":364},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"储能装置没有问题欸。","id":365,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"伟大的梅尔小姐，您亲自设计的装置怎么可能会出现问题？我从来好得不得了！请看，充沛的热力正在我的体内激情四射地流淌！","id":367,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"那第二次攻击的提前是什么原因？","id":369,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"让我想想......难道是武器能量输出逻辑出错？","id":370,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":371},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"你们来之前我就查过了，逻辑本身还是好的。","id":372,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"咦，本身是好的？梅尔，你的意思是，还是有一些小问题吧？","id":374,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"唔，我不确定这是不是问题。你自己看。","id":376,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":377},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"效率......提升？虽然只有几个百分点，但Thermal-EX释放每次攻击的能量损耗都显著减少了吧？","id":378,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这充满惊喜的迭代——梅尔，你真是我的好伙伴！","id":380,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer","focus":"2","id":381},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"先......先别这么激动啊。这优化不是我做的。我这段时间有多忙，你不是知道的吗？","id":382,"figure":"char_242_mayer"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"char_242_mayer","focus":"1","id":383},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"也对，上回拜托你考虑机械臂自动化逻辑的改进设计，你都说没法排期。","id":384,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":385},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"还是直接提问好了——Thermal-EX，最近有谁动过你吗？","id":386,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":387},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"这个问题很简单！与我关系最亲密的，除了可爱的可露希尔小姐和智慧的梅尔小姐，当然是无敌的博士！","id":388,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"博士，你现在开始对机械作业平台和人工智能感兴趣了吗？","id":390,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"392","text":"我什么都没做。"},{"id":"392","text":"......"},{"id":"392","text":"我们只是相处时间久一点而已。"}],"values":[],"id":391},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":392},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":393},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我想也不会是你做的。","id":394,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"毕竟，我和梅尔只是忙得没空睡觉，你和凯尔希过得就像一天有四十八小时。","id":395,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"可露希尔小姐你放心！有我在，我会让博士有限的睡梦更热一点点！","id":397,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":398},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":399},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"诶？！","id":400,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"更热一点点......","id":401,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"原来如此。之前一个月你都在干这个？","id":403,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":404},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"我们罗德岛是一艘划时代的舰船！唯一美中不足的是，干员宿舍在夜间的温度还不够热！","id":405,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":406},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......对某些干员来说，是有一点。赫默也跟我说过，有时候晚上睡觉会不自觉地想要变出羽毛。","id":407,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"哦？我的节能方案影响到大家的睡眠质量了吗？","id":409,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":410},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":411},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":412},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"啊——啊嚏。","id":413,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"没办法，我们船上的人越来越多，同时启用的舱室数量也在增长，供能效率方面需要不断迭代，这可不是一项轻松的工作。","id":414,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":415},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"我也想为可露希尔小姐分忧！所以那天，在听到博士半夜打喷嚏以后，我就做了一个决定！","id":416,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"我想将自己体内的热量分一点给博士，还有其他怕冷的干员！","id":417,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"419","text":"一开始差点把我房间炸了。"},{"id":"419","text":"我险些被一发烤熟。"}],"values":[],"id":418},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":419},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":420},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"抱歉，博士！第一次是我缺乏经验！过于火热的我，一时间难以区分熔化敌人和温暖朋友的区别！","id":421,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":422},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":423},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呜哇，我和可露希尔可没有给你设置暖炉功能的发热逻辑！","id":424,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":425},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"梅尔你这一下蹦起来差点没把我撞到墙上去......","id":426,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":427},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":428},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"可露希尔，你难道不激动吗？Thermal-EX他超越了我们为他设计的功能！","id":429,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":430},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"嗯，我听着呢。","id":431,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"因为他想给博士当暖炉，所以每天晚上都在持续使用热力法术，导致需求频繁充能，消耗太大，线路过载，我的节能计划报废——","id":432,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":433},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":434},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":435},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"诶，诶诶？","id":436,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":437},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":438},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"Thermal-EX，你自己改变了自己的能量输出逻辑？！","id":439,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":440},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"美丽的可露希尔小姐，感谢您的热情拥抱！您说的没错，这件事做起来并不容易，但我始终记得自己是凝聚了你们智慧的杰出机器人！","id":441,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"一点小小的挫折——包括险些将博士烤熟——并不会打击我的信心。经过一段时间的尝试，我还是找到了方法！","id":442,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"容我骄傲地说，只要能给博士和其他干员带来温暖，这点努力根本算不了什么。","id":443,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"1","id":444},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"这是......机器人的自我进化？Lancet-2和Castle-3身上都没有发生过。","id":445,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#6"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"447","text":"在叙拉古的时候也是类似情况吧？"}],"values":[],"id":446},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":447},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","id":448},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"博士，您的猜想一如既往地正确！","id":449,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"就像我刚才说的，随着我越来越好地为您和其余干员提供供暖服务，我对如何控制力量仿佛有了更深刻的领悟。","id":450,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"当时我的神经依旧处于麻痹状态，可我依然感知到您陷入了危险。","id":451,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"对您的担忧令我本该沉寂的内心重新燃起了火热的力量。当我有所意识的时候，我已经向敌人发出了那道冲击波！","id":452,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"虽然在战场上，我发光发热的时间依然短暂，但我还是想竭尽——不，超出全力地帮助您！","id":453,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#6","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":454},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":455},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"可露希尔，你都听见了吗？这些话都说明Thermal-EX是在自主意愿的驱使下完成了功能的突破。这甚至不是巧合哎！","id":456,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我要——我要记下来。把这些情况记录一下。","id":457,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":458},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"Thermal-EX，我想让你帮我做一些实验，可以吗？","id":459,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":460},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"乐意之至，我亲爱的梅尔小姐！","id":461,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#4","id":462},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"咪波，咪波，把我的设备拿来——","id":463,"figure":"char_242_mayer#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#4","focus":"1","id":464},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"梅尔。","id":465,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":466},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"可露希尔，你拦着我干什么？","id":467,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"你也是研究者，这很可能是你对智能机器人研究的重大突破，你不激动么？","id":469,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我很激动啊，你看不出来？","id":471,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":472},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"噢，你话都变少了。确实，你现在超激动的。","id":473,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":474},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"嗯。可是你说的有一句话，我不是特别同意。","id":475,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":476},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗯？哪句？","id":477,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"1","id":478},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"——这不是巧合。","id":479,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"我想，这对Thermal-EX来说，的确不是巧合。","id":480,"figure":"char_007_closre_1"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"482","text":"但Thermal-EX能拥有这样独特的个性，这本身是一个巧合。"}],"values":[],"id":481},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":482},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":483},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"博士，你真的不考虑下从事机械作业平台和人工智能研究吗？","id":484,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":485},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"唔，Thermal-EX的个性，也是可露希尔设计的吧。","id":486,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":487},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"说是设计，其实也就是设置了一些基础参数。之后他加工的每一部分信息、进行的每一项决策，早就不是我控制的啦。","id":488,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":489},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"这么说的话......","id":490,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":491},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"让Thermal-EX突破极限的，不是我们俩身为设计者的意志，也不是技术，而是它自己。","id":492,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","name2":"char_376_therex_1","focus":"2","id":493},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"我还记得可露希尔小姐对我说的第一句话哦！“你是Thermal-EX，你要有力量！”","id":494,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":495},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Thermal-EX","text":"对我来说，力量就是热量！没有最热，只有更热！我始终都会走在变得更热更强的路上！","id":496,"figure":"char_376_therex_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_376_therex_1","name2":"char_242_mayer#3","focus":"2","id":497},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"呜哇，这发言真是干劲满满呀。","id":498,"figure":"char_242_mayer#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":499},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"就是这样——我的身体也跟着热起来了哦！","id":500,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_007_closre_1#2","id":501},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"可露希尔","text":"博士，梅尔，让我们一起见证Thermal-EX带来更强劲的热量冲击吧！","id":502,"figure":"char_007_closre_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":503},{"type":"Character","id":504},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":505},{"type":"Image","id":506}],"characters":["工程干员","可露希尔","医药公司代表","Thermal-EX","干员直尺","斑点","守林人","黑帮A","黑帮B","梅尔"]}